# Optional: Google Analytics 4 (visitor tracking)
# Create a property at https://analytics.google.com → Admin → Data streams → Web
# Then paste the Measurement ID (starts with G-):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in ONE of the options below.
# Restart `npm run dev` after saving.

# --- Option A (easiest, free) ---
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com
# 2. Enter jewelsphy@gmail.com and create an access key
# 3. Paste it here:
WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=

# --- Option B (Resend) ---
# 1. Go to https://resend.com and create a free API key
# 2. Paste it here (can send to your Gmail using onboarding@resend.dev):
# RESEND_API_KEY=
# RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=JewelSphy <onboarding@resend.dev>
